content.detailedDescription: I was on the 8th deck balcony of royal caribbeans enchantment of the seas at 7am in the morning of january 30, 2017.  i was enjoying the scenery of biscayne bay as my cruise ship headed to the cruise port of miami, fl as was my usual custom when returning home from a cruise..At approximately 7:10 am i saw the familiar blinking lights of an airplane approaching the miami airport. i heard the usual sound of a plane . less than a minute later i noticed a very bright reddish orange orb of  light ascend over a building. at first i thought it was a light fixed on top of the building but it continued to slowly ascend until it hovered directly in the path of the plane.  i became frightened at that point thinking that i was about to witness a plane crash and suddenly the light ascended so fast to avoid the plane that it didnt seem real.  i couldn't believe that it moved and stopped so quickly, it hovered quite a few feet over the plane, staying there until the plane was well past that spot. it stayed there for about 30 seconds more and then disappeared so quickly.  it disappeared in a flash. it made no sound. it did not leave a trail or make a break in the clouds. it was just gone. the entire incident happened within a five minute period. i stood on the balcony a few minutes more in horrified amazement wondering what i had just witnessed. i hope to find out if anyone else actually saw what i had just seen.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Reddish orange bright light flew up toward an airplane, hovered before it reached the plane, quickly ascended to avoid the plane, hovered again, quickly ascended out of sight

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i like to sit out back and stargaze. we often see unexplainable objects in the sky and have started looking for these. tonight we saw a bright oval object appear overhead very high up...If i had to guess, i'd say 15,000 ft. but it is just a guess. the object was traveling east very fast when it lit up. it literally made a hard 90 degree turn to the south-west as the light faded it sped off across the sky and out of sight...The event lasted only seconds but we both saw it. very exciting observation!
content.summary: Star gazing saw oval white light moving east very fast then turned 90 deg to sw

content.detailedDescription: I was talking with my husband, looking towards a window when i noticed a small bright light through the upper half of the window. i thought at first it must be a plane or perhaps venus. the object stayed bright white throughout the sighting but pulsated. it flashed off a few times but only for a second. i realized it could not be a plane because from where i was sitting, it remained in the same pane of glass in the upper half of our window. my husband said it was a street light but it was too high to be a streetlight. he tried to take a photo with his ipad and i went to get my sony camera. i took eight pictures through the glass and screen between 7:28 and 7:37. i checked to see if the pictures came out and what they looked like when i zoomed in. i continued to check if the object was still there and if moved. the object remained in the same place but it went from circular to egg shaped, from my vantage point. i saw another object that traveled towards the brighter and larger object that i was watching. it did not join the larger object and did not stay. it was there and then it wasn't there. at 8:00 (20:00) i went downstairs with my husband to get some dinner but decided to go outside to take a few more pictures. by then the stars were out and orion's belt was visible higher up but in the same easterly direction as the object i was observing. i took four photos between 8:18 and 8:20. the object appeared a little higher against the pine tree. street lights and car lights are visible in the photos in addition to the object and the stars. i don't know when the object left. it was gone by the time we finished eating. i tried to take a video but so far haven't found it on my camera. i probably didn't do it correctly. i have seen things that i can't explain while on airplanes. i am curious but not afraid of the sightings.
content.summary: I saw a bright light through the window which didn't move during the twenty minutes i observed it. i went outside 40 minutes later and it was still visible.

content.detailedDescription:
i have already reported this ufo but recently going back and looking at the pictures i noticed my phone was set up on the live picture mood on my iphone 6 but while taking this picture the live feature was turned off also i noticed that on the satellite image from my phone i could identify the object. i identified few other objects in the water from the  satellite picture from the same day that i saw the object that looked very strange they are deep in the water but they are not mountains, object looks like it's glowing under the water , very large . 
 i took this picture while walking at the geo park at taipei taiwan i did not notice the object until after i looked at my pictures .
content.summary: Yellowish object  shooting out of water, picture and  satellite picture

content.detailedDescription:
On january 17 2017, i was travelling west on interstate 10, in new mexico. 
when i came to the town of akela, i spotted a dark, oval object, hovering above the little florida mountains, to the southwest.
the object must have been at least a 100 feet in diameter.
i was able to take a 13 mpix photograph of the object which is not included in this report.
i was still able to watch the object when i then moved on to deming. 
when i came to deming i was still able to observe the object to the south.
but the object then appeared smaller, and was possibly moving away. 
it then became dark, and i was no longer able to see the object. 
as to what this could have been, my conclusion is that this object could only have been an airship or an ufo. 
it did not look the least bit like a plane, helicopter or any other known celestial object. 
i do not know if there was an airship in this area at that time. 
but pherhaps somebody else can answer that question.
content.summary: Travelling west on interstate 10 in new mexico.

content.detailedDescription:
I was at kelley's beach bargara testing my new camera (canon 7d mk3)and filming the beach. it was months later that i noticed this object appear out of the top of the frame at high speed. at first i thought it was a meteor but it seems to change direction. i can also see another small object close to the main object as it comes into frame. it's moving extremely fast and seems very high but it could also be very small and close. 
i thought the change of direction could be to it skimming the atmosphere?
the object it moving so fast it would have been almost impossible to view with the naked eye.
content.summary: Was testing new camera and only spotted object after playback.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving back to midland from school in odessa. when i saw a white object in the sky in front of me. it didn't look like a plane, it kinda looked like a big piece of paper but at some points it looked like a sphere. it didn't look like it had any sort of wings or lights. at some points it looked like it totally disappeared but that could have been because of my eyes or the fact i was driving.
content.summary: Unknown object crossed my path while driving.

content.detailedDescription:
When i first noticed this light i was walking my dog in the back yard of our home. it was one of those double take moments. i glanced you as i usually look at the sky/stars and was headed back inside w/ the dog and i quick looked back because what i saw didn't belong there. at first i thought airplane, but it did have any flashing lights like all planes have & it was exstreamly bright.
i stood and watched it for a couple minutes and at first it didn't seem to be moving. then i noticed a side to side motion and it seemed as though it was headed in our direction.
i quick, got in the house and called for my wife to come look at it. she had the same thoughts. plane, no... it looks like it's moving side to side ect... the movement was very subtle and it was going anywhere. i'm the last guy to quick grab my cellphone and take photos or video but this light hung around long enough for me to think about getting my binoculars and take video of this weird light.
then it bacame more bizarre when i looked at it with the binoculars and st that point i knew it wasn't a star. we took videos of it on my cell phone. when we reviewed the videos, it looked like a spinning donut with a lot of different colored lights that move so fast you couldn't see most of the colors by eye! with the video zoomed in, it morphed in and out of shapes. my wife and i both looking at each other with our mouths hanging open not knowing what to think!
i went back outside to see if it was still there and it had moved a good deal of distance and gave me a tree to gage its movement and it startled me. i have to say, that's not done easily! but it didn't move like ya might see other people's encounters and videos. it was very suddle but very obvious when it did.
i again drug my wife outside in the cold and she was watching it and i heard her gasp! she saw it move like i did!
this light hung around for a long while. i went in and out as it was very cold, wind blowing ect.. probably about 5 degrees with windchill. however, i took videos each time i went out until when i finally went out and it was gone!
we talked about it all the rest of the night. both of us trying to find a logical answer to this strange light. stuff like, it's probably government, could it be a drone ect...  thing is, we have the view of air liners, commercial jets and there is an airport somewhere, not sure where exactly but there are a lot of small planes that take a certain pathetic taking off or landing (?).
on one of my trips out in the freezing weather i observed an commercial passenger plane flying about as high as they fly and it almost crossed paths. it was close enough that i remember thinking that the people on that plane had to see it, specially the pilots. when this happened it was pretty obvious that this light was a lot higher than the plane and even gave me the feeling it could be out of our atmosphere.
the thing that baffles us is the videos i took. the shape and color changing that occurs is just crazy!
i was in the # 1 combat ready unit stationed in the us and spent most of my life in law enforcement. my last job being a police officer. i am a trained observer and its driving me crazy as to what this light is!
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Bright light that didn't belong. when using binoculars, flash sharp rays of various colors & w/ cell phone video looked like a donut flashing multitude of bright colors

content.detailedDescription: I was home leaving to pick my two boys from church school. an unusual noise coming overhead from the south got my attention. the group came out from the trees at about three to five hundred feet above ground heading north.They were traveling at about forty miles per hour in a north-westerly direction. they were almost completely silent, just a low frequency hum and the buffeting of the wind as they passed.They were tethered together and no doors or windows were visible. this sighting happened on may tenth, 1966 at eleven thirty in the morning.
content.summary: Five triangular  shaped ufo's five to seven feet thick tethered together being pulled along by the first.

content.detailedDescription: My son and i were leaning on the back of my truck on a very dark night when out of nowhere just above us an object 500 ft approx.Flew over our heads.I have seen many sightings in over 50 years but this was a first.Never reporting any of my sightings until this one and the next one to follow.This one had a distent sound. it sounded just like those jeti swords,a loud curdiling sound. still get goose bumps today.
content.summary: Object flew over me and my sons head he is 49 yrs old

content.detailedDescription:
As reported to asd by phone: last night as i was getting ready to get into my car i had a feeling i should look up for some reason, and as i did so i noticed a very bright light moving from past kansas city from the sw headed directly towards me. the object flew directly above me, then continued on towards the ne in a straight line path. it was a circular shape, was lit up all over like a light, had no wings or tail and no other lights. there was no sound or vibration. i realized that it was not a conventional aircraft.

note from asd: there were two other sightings in the area reported last night at the same time.
content.summary: Large sphere shaped light traveling faster than a fighter jet

content.detailedDescription: There wad what i thought to be a helicopter hovering outside my window 12/13/16 for an extraordinary amount of time so i pointed my camcorder through the window and got 2 20 second clips of a translucent craft with beings inside. i put the video on my laptop and took photos of interesting frames.
content.summary: Filmed translucent disc hovering outside my apt window in denver 12/13/16

content.altitude: Treetop, 500 Feet or Less, Over 500 Feet (no cloudcover)
content.detailedDescription: First saw directly behind my home over tree. i thought venus looks weird then noticed venus was more toward the west, and this object was due south. it had what looked like a strip of lights which changed colors. blue, green, white or yellow and red. it was still for a min or so the began moving higher. then it abrubtly turned left and moved across the sky before coming to a stop in the western sky. i heard no noise. it stayed in the western sky for a while. still the lights looked like a strip, kind of pulsating and changing colors in what seemed a random order to me. finally it turned all red or red/orange and looked like a ball then disappeared. i tried to get better pictures but my phones camera stopped working. very weird. have no idea what it was.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: At first thought it was venus, but it changed colors and i located venus. looked like a strip of lights going around craft and changing colors. hovered then moved up, the abruptly to the left. turned all red, then disappeared.

content.detailedDescription:
In the back yard while i was taking our dog out, i saw many color lights coming from what seen to be a star, in the night sky, it seems like a portal after looking thru camera. one of the sighting was round with just one color while a long black ufo passed in front of the portal. the other portals where flashing all kinds of colors. a lot of activity of lights.
i kept saying "this is crazy. i can't believe this. what are these lights?
i have never lost sight, they are out there 3, 4 or 5 times a week. they appear in different places in the sky. sometimes north, n/e, east, e/s/e, two or 3 of them! they are coming in and out of the portal!  
i know why they are here and what they want.
content.summary: Pilots ships orbe many flashing colors black object above portal.

content.detailedDescription: On september 17 1976 my father had taken me deer hunting we were hunting with bow and arrow.  i was 15 almost 16 but he would always walk me in the dark through the woods to my treestand he always told me to sit still here i've seen deer here.My father was a quite the hunter, hunted in canada as well.Anyway i've never spoke of this before i've always felt it was supposed to be a secret somehow. it's been 40 years but i remember it like it just happened. my walk me through the woods as usual we found my treestand it wasn't like yet because my father used a flashlight to show me it he told me he been down there looking there was plenty of deer that will be coming out of the soybean field around 25 yards from my treestand on the edge of the wood line as soon as the sun came up. and he'd be on the opposite side of the field in his stand the field was probably 300 yards wide. anyway i got into my stand my father went out of sight maybe 45 minutes my eyes adjusted to the sun starting to rise had been a calm day no wind blowing no rain no nothin then i heard up the tree line the leaves on the trees rustling i looked up there the small trees were shaking back and forth making the leaves fall out i watched it has the tree started shaking closer and closer and closer to me as i looked up in the tree i fell what i can only playing as if you're driving down the highway on a hot day that hazy look you see on the road it was above the trees 15-20 feet coming down the tree line towards me i could see the sky but it was hazy and swirling  i was in a tree i'd say 16 inches in diameter when it got you my tree my tree started to shake i grabbed  it to hold on because it was shaking very hard meantime i was looking up it i'd say when i looked up at it it took two minutes for it to finally go past me over my head no more than 10 feet the only noise it made was what's the swishing of the wind and leaves i'm guessing it was 50 yards to 80 yards round as i looked up i could see the edge after it went by trees quite shaking and  the sky cleared up.  i sat and watch the tree shake and wimbrow until it was out of my sight i couldn't see no more trees shake it i know how my father was if i would have told him i probably would have got laughed at by him and his hunting club friends the only thing he said to me that morning around 10:30 he came back he said my face looked like it had gotten windburned.It stayed kinda reddish for a couple days. that's it.Thanks for listening feel good to tell it somehow
content.summary: something big an round flew 10 feet over my head while i was in a greedy and it was transparent

content.detailedDescription:
Just returned home from gas station. looked up as i got out of spouse car and noticed a bright orb near the moon and noting that it was not normal i watched as it slowly traveled north. i continued watching as it traveled well to the north before it just blinked out. it never changed light or intensity as it traveled toward me, overhead then away from me to the north.
when it got to about the same distance from me to the north as it was from the south it just turned off and was gone.
content.summary: Bright white orb traveling from south to north

content.detailedDescription: Standing on the deck in front of my house talking with my fiance and spotted the object. it caught my attention because it was unlike any other aircraft i've seen. we both pulled our phones out and filmed the object until it disappeared behind the treeline. i'm not saying it's "alien" bbut i've never seen anything like it. i'd like to know what it was.
content.summary: Starlike, bright orb flying straight, definitely not a plane

content.detailedDescription: I was driving on hwy 99 n, just pat fry rd. it was to the ne ahead of me.  there was a flash of light and then a yelp wish green tail, like a shooting star. my coworker saw the same thing and she was 4 miles in front of me.
content.summary: Flash and trail of yellow-green light. fast speed.

content.detailedDescription: At first i was on the phone with my girlfriend and i saw a very bright fluorescent light shining through the window and i looked out the window and this object that a very sharp turn and that's when the bright light dimmed and i seen other colorful lights in a circular motion and i thought to myself this cannot be a plane or a jet the way the lights were so very bright and at first i felt nervous but not too scared because i've seen one before in this same area not so long ago
content.summary: Appeared out of nowhere then did a sharp turn with a bright florescent light and flew by quick over building

content.detailedDescription: I was outside looking at venus over the moon. directly below that at probably 20 feet altitude i saw a red light followed by a white light maybe 10 to 15 feet apart moving through the trees in a northward direction.  they moved from my left to right at probably ten miles per hour.  they disappeared after about 10 seconds.  i went back in the house and about 3 to 5 minutes later i went back out and again saw a red light in approximately the same place but maybe a little further away than i saw it before and it again moved from my left to right and disappeared after about 5 seconds.  i live on a wooded hill and these lights were too high to be a person with lights and way too low to be a plane or helicopter even if the object was farther than it seemed. after the woods there is a swampy area but if i was seeing something that far away, the object would be in the swamp not above it.It was totally silent.
content.summary: Lights moving through trees maybe 20 feet altitude.

content.detailedDescription: It was thursday night january 26th, 2017 at approximately 9:00 p.M. my mother and i were driving from winnipeg to my mother's house just west of carman, mb. when we were driving about a mile away from her home, my mother asked,"is that a star ahead of us on the left?"  i replied by saying,"yeah, it sure looks like a star but it's too low to be a star. look it's actually moving closer. look now, from here it looks like it's hovering right over your house!"  as we were getting closer it looked like it was brighter but it was also moving west. my mother stated,"jody, what are we looking at?"  i said to her,"i think it's a real ufo. look it's hovering and then taking off again." by the time we made it to the driveway, the huge light was about 2-3 miles away. we kept looking westward through the trees in the bush and my mother said,"i can stil see it." i looked as well and we could still see it out in the distance. my mother wanted to get in the car again and follow this massive light. i told her that it's too far already, we'll never catch up to it so we didn't bother chasing it. it didn't look like any man made lighting and there's no way it was a drone with lights on it. it was simply too huge of an object and it resembled a bright star that could hover and move very fast. what we both saw was very impressive and quite remarkable. this is a sighting that we both will never forget.
content.summary: We thought it was a star but it lowered it's position and hovered, then started moving w.

content.detailedDescription: I took this on jan 28th 2017 at around 2:30pm  with an iphone 7 while playing golf at the okeeheelee golf course in west palm beach fl.  i saw a floating chrome sphere moving very slowly and started filming. i only filmed for a short time as we were moving on since there were people waiting behind us. the object made no sound...It almost looked like a giant balloon, bigger than a car. after watching it on video i noticed that at the 6th second there was another orb passing through it from right to left at an incredible speed. i'm a student pilot and i'm fairly familiar with aircraft and i'm quite certain that these objects were no helicopters or planes.
content.summary: Hovering orb, then a second passing through it at high speed

content.detailedDescription: I went outside in the backyard to smoke a cigarette and i immediately  saw the 2 weird looking lights so i grabbed my phone from my jacket pocket and started filming it. this time i have the original unedited video which i am submitting, sorry about the audio i was talking to myself.
content.summary: I just went outside to have a cigarette and i saw 2 weird lights.

content.detailedDescription:
On january 29, 2017, at approximately 2010 hrs, i looked outside my kitchen/family room to the east.  it was dark, and the sky was clear.  i observed a yellowish light, much larger than a single star, hovering in the air east-south-east of my location.  i would guess that it was approximately 3/4 - 1 mile distant, about 1,000 - 1,500 feet above the ground.  it had an oval configuration, and was stationary in the sky. it glowed with a yellowish-white light. there had been a westerly wind all day, sometimes gusting to 80 kph, but at this time of the evening, the air was still.  at first i supposed that it was a helicopter, but it made no sound whatsoever; the evening was perfectly silent.  from that distance, i would have been able to hear a helicopter clearly.  i went back into the house and retrieved a pair of binoculars, and viewed the object through them.  as i focused the binoculars, i could see four smaller objects, two of which were visible only as single, white lights, one visible as a single red light, and one visible as a pair of white lights.  they were all very small, and flitting about the object like flies.  the fourth object appeared as if it might have been triangular in shape, but it was difficult to ascertain.  i dropped the binoculars down and called to my wife to come out and see, and as i kept my eyes on the object, a second object of the same configuration as the first appeared beside and below it, on its right-hand side.  there was no dark shape that suddenly illuminated, it simply appeared out of nothing.  both objects hovered together for a moment as my wife came outside and observed them with me.  after about two minutes of the objects hovering together, the original object began to move slowly to the north while emitting a flashing red light in its underside.  at this time, the smaller lights flitting about the first object disappeared. it was difficult to see if they went into the first object, or simply blinked out.  the second object remained hovering in a stationary position while the first object moved slowly to the north and disappeared behind a house across the alley from my own. i watched the second object for about ten more minutes, until it finally began to follow the path of the first object and move slowly to the north as well.  it took about a minute before it too disappeared behind the same house.

the objects were hovering in the center of the flight path for our local international airport, in the same position as a previous object spotted on january 26th (mufon file #81752).  planes had been taking off from the airport all day, but now, while i observed the objects, there were no flights departing the airport.  around 2100 hrs, departing flights resumed.  about an hour after the sighting, the westerly wind picked up once more.  i do not know if there is a correlation between these two events and the objects.
content.summary: 2 objects glowed yellow with red flashing light.  one was visible with several smaller lights buzzing around. second object appeared, then first flew away.  then second object flew away.

content.detailedDescription:
My husband and i were returning home from a day in new braunfels/gruene area (about 30 miles north of san antonio) driving eastbound on interstate 10. i was on my facebook via smartphone until my husband who was driving asked me about these lights on the drivers side. i told him they were cell towers and waited for the car to position itself to see a shadow or outline of a pole....There was no pole. i said maybe it's a plane or a helicopter and then he commented on the light pattern was not characteristic of a plane or helicopter, since he was a ndt inspector in the us air force in the early 2000s and worked inspection off welds and aircraft issues all the time and is familiar with various aircraft. the lights truly looked circular, giving him and i the indication that  this was no type of craft we've ever seen.

we stopped at the nearest exit (exit 617-kingsbury) and proceeded to take pictures or videos with our camera phones (picture quality was extremely poor). to our amazement there were at least 20 additional crafts or lights at the time in perfect zig-zag formation and then gliding across both lanes of i-10 e/w in the night sky. as they glided away from the westbound lane one by one blinked and disappeared. i was flabbergasted and told my husband that this was impossible that any craft to just disappear.

the next few moments of our encounter was just as exciting...Now the light/crafts were arriving in clusters of 3-4 at a time and disappearing just the same. my husband moved the car to get a better view of the southern horizon where the craft/lights were coming from and i noticed a pinkish/purplish hue of mist or smoke coming out of the treeline after the last one light disappeared. my husband was concerned that it was a fire and wanted to leave before it caught up to us.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Fleet of ufos over interstate 10e

content.detailedDescription: on my way home from work i stopped at the grocery  at about 530 or so.   it was a gloomy afternoon and i noticed behind me a rainbow.    my husband gave me a brand-new phone so i took three photographs of the rainbow.  i only just realized there was something in two of the photographs.    after enlarging the photos on my phone, both objects appear to be  disc shapes with lights  that go around the objects.  i did not notice them at the time i had taken the photographs  with my new i phone 6s.   only the first two photos show the two objects. i included the third photo because it shows the rest of the rainbow.  the last two photos are only close-ups of the first two photos that show the objects within.
content.summary: two objects appeared in my pictures   i did not realize they were there until later showing off my new phone

content.detailedDescription: Was at the ocean beach pier in san diego. we heard two really quick loud booms one after another. a large gust of wind hit us and the ground shook. it was reported by many people all over san diego, from the beach into santee and by the mexico boarder. the media looked into possible sonic booms, any military air crafts, any bombing off shore and earthquakes. they found nothing to explain this. so we wonder if it could have been something not of this earth?
content.summary: Two quick loud booms, large gust of wind (at the beach where i was) and the ground shook all over san diego

content.detailedDescription: I was driving with my dog late night coming back home when suddenly, in front of my car, appeared out of thin air a ball of light about 300 ft. from the front of my windshield. 300 ft above the ground. this object can manipulate light because the light that it was admitting ended around its horizon, as if it were in some invisible bubble. in the middle of this bubble of light was a sphere, the most purist led light i've ever seen. i say led because it had a bluish tint. the sphere itself was like a ball of plasma that was emitting light. very bright and white with bluish tint, but the whole bubble of light was very dim. hard to explain since i've never seen anything do that before with that kind of manipulation of light. this bubble with this sphere inside of it, did not reflect light on any surface around me. it was as if it didn't want to be seen. there were people doing things in their front yard in the area, but didn't even notice it. two young guys noticed it and started hollering and yelling, amazed at the ball of light they have just seen when i went around the block. the horizon of light around this object grew and then shrunk, about 6-8 times before disappearing in front of my eyes. i then drove my car around the block, that's when i saw two guys amazed at what they had just seen. they yelled out, " wow did you just see content.detailedDescription:
Last night i was driving home at about 6:30 (january 29th) and noticed the moon had a smiley face and i decided to take a pic to send to my girlfriend.  the first pic i zoomed in and it wasn't super clear so i decided to try again.  i was stopped and had my camera held out the window.  just as i was taking the second pictured i noticed a light zoom in and out of the picture..... it was so fast i wouldn't have noticed had i not been taking the picture.... literally a fraction of a second... then i took another picture.... when i looked at them it turns out i caught what i saw on the photo.... pretty amazing.  i don't think it was a shooting star (none were visible in the perfectly clear sky nor an asteroid as it was moving so fast and it was clearly in our atmosphere and low.... hmmm!!
ufo?
content.summary: While taking a photo of the moon with a happy face i noticed a fast-moving light, which i managed to catch in picture.
